import React from 'react'
import {
    List , 
    Datagrid,
    TextField ,
    DateField,
    EditButton,
    DeleteButton 
    }  from 'react-admin'

const PostList = (props) => {
    return <List {...props}>
           <Datagrid>
               <TextField source="id" />
               <TextField source="title" />
               <DateField source="publishedAt" />
               <EditButton basePath="/posts" />
               <DeleteButton basePath="/posts" />
           </Datagrid>
    </List>
}

export default PostList
